---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="25岁复盘 · 查询手册"
  description="25岁（生日到生日）的年度复盘与应对手册：可跳转、可折叠原文。"
  robots="noindex, nofollow"
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero glass-card animate-on-load">
        <div class="hero__badge">PRIVATE · LIFE REVIEW</div>
        <h1 class="hero__title">25岁复盘</h1>
        <p class="hero__desc">
          一份给未来自己的「查询手册」：按场景卡片、早期预警、好的一天配方、边界脚本、情绪-需求地图等整理，支持跳转与原文折叠。
        </p>
        <div class="hero__actions">
          <a class="hero__btn hero__btn--primary btn-animate" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_review.html">
            打开查询手册
          </a>
          <a class="hero__btn btn-animate" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_warnings.html">
            早期预警
          </a>
          <a class="hero__btn btn-animate" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_boundaries.html">
            关系与边界
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__hint">
          手册页快捷键：<span class="kbd">Ctrl</span>+<span class="kbd">K</span> 快速跳转；右下角「跳转/专注/设置」可切换暗色与字号。
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid">
        <a class="card glass-card interactive-hover" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_good_day.html">
          <div class="card__k">G</div>
          <div class="card__t">好的一天配方</div>
          <div class="card__d">起床—环境—输入—输出—休息的共同结构。</div>
        </a>
        <a class="card glass-card interactive-hover" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_emotions.html">
          <div class="card__k">E</div>
          <div class="card__t">情绪-需求地图</div>
          <div class="card__d">常见情绪背后的真实需要 + 替代满足方式。</div>
        </a>
        <a class="card glass-card interactive-hover" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_desires.html">
          <div class="card__k">D</div>
          <div class="card__t">渴望与追求</div>
          <div class="card__d">你想要怎样的生活（附原文证据）。</div>
        </a>
        <a class="card glass-card interactive-hover" href="/age-25/dashboard/age_25_anti_vision.html">
          <div class="card__k">A</div>
          <div class="card__t">反向愿景</div>
          <div class="card__d">最不想要的生活（附原文证据）。</div>
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="files glass-card">
        <h2 class="files__title">原始文件</h2>
        <ul class="files__list">
          <li>
            <a class="files__link" href="/age-25/age-25-review.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              age-25-review.md
            </a>
            <span class="files__muted">（含嵌入原文段落）</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="files__note">
          说明：为了让手册页能实时读取，Markdown 会作为站点静态文件被访问；已默认设置 <span class="kbd">noindex</span>，并从 sitemap 排除。
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .hero {
    margin: 46px 0 18px;
    padding: 26px 22px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -120px;
    background: radial-gradient(
        circle at 20% 25%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 22%, transparent),
        transparent 55%
      ),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 15%, rgba(77, 99, 167, 0.16), transparent 52%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 85%, rgba(45, 156, 122, 0.16), transparent 58%);
    pointer-events: none;
    filter: blur(2px);
  }

  .hero > * {
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero__badge {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.95;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .hero__title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 44px);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .hero__desc {
    margin: 12px 0 16px;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.82;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .hero__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 24%, transparent);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
  }

  .hero__btn:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 34%, transparent);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.32);
  }

  .hero__btn--primary {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 40%, transparent);
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 16%, transparent),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)
    );
  }

  .hero__hint {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.72;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .kbd {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
      "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin: 18px 0 18px;
  }

  .card {
    padding: 16px 16px 14px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .card__k {
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 14%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 28%, transparent);
  }

  .card__t {
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .card__d {
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.74;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .files {
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 16px 16px 14px;
    margin: 8px 0 46px;
  }

  .files__title {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .files__list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .files__link {
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 46%, transparent);
  }

  .files__link:hover {
    border-bottom-style: solid;
  }

  .files__muted {
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.68;
    margin-left: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .files__note {
    margin: 10px 0 0;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.68;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
